OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FManchester Airport cannot  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftake shortcuts on security 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F- Shapps                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government cannot take "shortcuts  
OL,6, on security" to boost staff numbers at 
OL,7, Manchester Airport, Transport Secretary
OL,8, Grant Shapps has said.                 
OL,10,FThe airport has been beset with long   
OL,11,Fpassenger delays since mid-March and   
OL,12,Fsaid it was "facing staff shortages and
OL,13,Frecruitment challenges".               
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham  
OL,16,Fhas called for the government to speed 
OL,17,Fup the vetting process for new staff.  
OL,19,FMr Shapps said officials would not "cut
OL,20,Fcorners" when it came to safety.       
